category: Text Perl
requires: perl perl-Getopt-ArgvFile perl-YAML-Syck
sdesc: "Creates HTML from plain text"
ldesc: "Perl script and module that converts plain text to HTML. It 
supports headings, lists, simple character markup, and hyperlinking, and 
is highly customizable. Perl script and module that converts plain text 
to HTML.  It recognizes some of the apparent structure of the
source documents and attempts to mark that structure explicitly using
HTML."
